{"tid":1503242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求推】律師團隊可唔可以幫市民申請禁制令？","createTime":"2019-08-25T01:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:00:11.000Z","uid":268123,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cca98f04650e1d1e2e2f6d741002e27156003774","tid":1503242,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:47:51.000Z","msg":"就新屋嶺嘅「懷疑」虐待手足事件，當日又喺新屋嶺有手足係你Client 嘅律師們，有無可能為「於大型群眾運動中被捕人士」申請禁制令？<br />\n<br />\nPlantiff：於大型群眾運動中被捕人士<br />\nDependent：警務處處長<br />\n<br />\n要求： 所有「於大型群眾運動中被捕人士」須於被捕後、扣押前立即由醫院管理局或獨立第三方醫療專業人士於被捕現場首先驗傷<br />\n<br />\n理據：<br />\n1. 律師團隊懷疑「於大型群眾運動中被捕人士」有系統被虐待<br />\n2. 律師團隊持續會為現時及將來「於大型群眾運動中被捕人士」提供法律支援"},{"pid":"a33d5bc40aea04cee14b851899dab477471ee73b","tid":1503242,"uid":238708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:51:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e4bb8367fa3630698ff4e563008dea337ac5a38c","tid":1503242,"uid":245760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aef84f8352b06b3dfb3c266d9d25267b95b8c72","tid":1503242,"uid":231641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"825"},{"pid":"4c2de700e4a0da8ee31f00da7d30fac9b9892882","tid":1503242,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"72004752cd1ab2e769d4e87e8a476401ea389e2a","tid":1503242,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"508ebd7f4042ce72e4bb835f6ad66a13f9dae9ed","tid":1503242,"uid":98734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"500512a98358b04ff5a372fdaedf696bb83b9826","tid":1503242,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n推到律師團隊見到"},{"pid":"0ab36b23a6fcc369978be4f3a62bfcafea1bcd64","tid":1503242,"uid":231641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":